.DT
set_item_state
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_item_state

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_item_state -  This method sets the state/location of a specific quest item owned by a player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_item_state(mixed pl_name,
mixed item,
mixed state)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pl_name%^RESET%^ -   player object or name
%^BOLD%^item%^RESET%^ -      item object or identifier
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/item_tracker.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the state/location of a specific quest item
owned by a player.


If the item isn't actually owned by the player it returns 0
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_item_state(), delete_item(), save_all_item_states()

.EP

